{"tid":1760430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"生3胎可「免除1000萬貸款」！匈牙利爆結婚潮...創29年最高紀錄","createTime":"2019-11-28T08:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T15:17:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2fe24ad38b965da05424752aeea9c4952ef792","tid":1760430,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"匈牙利與日本、韓國等同樣面臨人口下降問題，為了鼓勵生育，匈牙利政府決定下重本，推出多項鼓勵民眾結婚以及生兒育女的優惠政策，其中包括夫婦只要生3胎（含以上），就可以「免除所有貸款」，結果在短短時間裡就讓當地結婚率暴增。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約郵報》報導，匈牙利總理奧班（Viktor Orb&aacute;n）為了扭轉人口下降趨勢，針對「家庭」推出了多項稅收優惠及相關政策，當局今年還推出一項新的「催生」計畫，「只要女性在41歲生日以前結婚，夫妻就可以獲得1000萬福林（約新台幣107萬元）的零利率貸款；若生2胎，則可以減免上述三分之一的借貸；生3胎便不用還這1000萬的貸款。」<br />\n<br />\n奧班表示，「在歐洲出生的孩子越來越少，每少一個孩子，就多讓一個移民進來，雖然從數據上確實有增加，但匈牙利需要的不是數字，而是真正的匈牙利之子。」因此，奧班除了減免貸款的政策外，也曾經推出「生4個小孩以上的女性可以終生免除個人所得稅」。<br />\n<br />\n匈牙利中央統計局（KSH）指出，今年1至9月內，結婚人數已經暴增了20％，是1990年以來的最高記錄。KSH統計員蓋齊（Gabriella Geczy）表示，「新計劃是於7月1日啟動，當時推出了各種新福利，而且前提是必須結婚。因此，我們認為這是最關鍵的解釋之一。」<br />\n<br />\n數據中也顯示，光是9月份，匈牙利新婚夫婦就比去年同月多了29％，是1979年以來最多人辦婚禮的9月。而本月初政府也表示，迄今已有5萬多對夫婦申請了新的貸款補貼，但今年的新婚夫婦是否會繼續生更多胎仍有待觀察。"},{"pid":"fb689afc4ba289ec4e564844d63bf91261ff8db7","tid":1760430,"uid":257448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e18f33c4f9a26dfdde3dc710c422ea70012b40f","tid":1760430,"uid":74022,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"真正的匈牙利之子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講得好"},{"pid":"babc8217e901b2d6e460379b14f913d7c32c1455","tid":1760430,"uid":22337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"得個廿六七萬港紙生3件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013e3fd5abce1c822b449c1c6b8cd96100e96ae5","tid":1760430,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"即刻多好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df645fbb62a6c12735d859fc54f616faeb8e3846","tid":1760430,"uid":110832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"babc8217e901b2d6e460379b14f913d7c32c1455","tid":1760430,"uid":22337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"得個廿六七萬港紙生3件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"可能果邊消費低<br />\n<br />\n但香港就一定行唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5a2e01746cbb9c46468deaad6a35d81f23bf1c","tid":1760430,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"香港地人人間屋都咁細<br />\n邊有可能生三件或以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6573726990ad6ba299401b21e1a8ede2b568d03d","tid":1760430,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"諗到地球未來 大家唔好再生啦樂嗎"},{"pid":"e000283f9c4b176c88d74098330bd337077aa64f","tid":1760430,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df645fbb62a6c12735d859fc54f616faeb8e3846","t